      "source": [
        "data.T.shape"
      ],
      "id": "22108963",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Matrix and vector operations\n"
      ],
      "id": "1c4956ce"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(2, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "19fa42ea",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(3, 2)\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "a3ca38a3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "a296dd2e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(B, A)"
      ],
      "id": "c17f049d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ B  # python 3.5 above"
      ],
      "id": "9ccc172e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A"
      ],
      "id": "8f098646",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "b5255bc4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "34fdd603",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.arange(3)\n",
        "x"
      ],
      "id": "a5eb2a15",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, x)"
      ],
      "id": "009afa60",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A.dot(x)"
      ],
      "id": "f8c6705b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ x"
      ],
      "id": "10d46f7e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "32e9a0de"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.random.rand(3, 3)\n",
        "B = np.random.rand(3, 3)"
      ],
      "id": "b5957c59",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = np.dot(B, np.dot(A, np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "7839b32e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = B.dot(A.dot(np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "68642f30",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A @ np.linalg.inv(B)"
      ],
      "id": "ac16775a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "0a6176a4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "3876e002",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "cf418c65",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "y = x[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "04180690",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(y.T, y)"
      ],
      "id": "f2933e55",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* Given two vectors, $\\mathbf{a} = [a_0, a_1, ..., a_M]~$ and $~\\mathbf{b} = [b_0, b_1, ..., b_N]$, $~$the outer product is $\\mathbf{a}^T\\mathbf{b}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
        " a_0 b_0 & a_0b_1 & \\cdots & a_0 b_N \\\\\n",
        " a_1 b_0 & \\cdots & \\cdots & a_1 b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\vdots  & \\ddots &        & \\vdots  \\\\\n",
        " a_M b_0 &        & \\ddots & a_M b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\end{pmatrix}\n",
        "$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "00824fb3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3])"
      ],
      "id": "2f8552b1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.outer(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "21bf9749",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "7e85844e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x[:, np.newaxis], x[np.newaxis, :])"
      ],
      "id": "bfa868a1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.ones((2, 2)), np.identity(2))"
      ],
      "id": "80535908",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.identity(2), np.ones((2, 2)))"
      ],
      "id": "df3c92fa",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "00824982"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "y = np.array([5, 6, 7, 8])"
      ],
      "id": "2f03022f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"n,n\", x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "dae5ac93",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "3c2a9bc5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "B = A.T"
      ],
      "id": "11aa234c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "c112a603",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.alltrue(np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B) == np.dot(A, B))"
      ],
      "id": "ac7a098f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    }
